  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00001",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四青袍、二院子、李敬犹同上。〖牌子〗。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00002",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李敬犹"
      ],
      "text": "本爵李敬犹。只为薛氏满门，尽入天牢，是我会同公卿，保救忠良，以赦薛氏之罪。奈武氏要杀尽忠良。又有一班权臣，屡进谗言，武氏竟要废帝。只是新君一废，可叹忠良无救也。",
      "text_length": 80
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00003",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "李敬犹"
      ],
      "text": "堪叹忠良屡代贤，薛刚惹祸胆包天。扶保唐室东西战，单戟匹马哪清闲。今朝诛戮无恩典，眼见公卿绝后传。昼夜忧愁难合眼，并无良谋救出监。思量心碎身体倦，步入书房观书篇。",
      "text_length": 80
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00004",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李敬犹"
      ],
      "text": "吓，晋君无道，听信屠岸贾之言，大肆荒淫。有上大夫赵宣子数谏，与岸贾两下结仇，每每设计，逼走了赵宣子，杀了赵氏一门。赵朔之妻，乃灵公之公主，住于冷宫，产下遗腹孤儿。宣子门下程婴，救出孤儿。岸贾四下缉拿。程婴将孤儿养藏别所，将亲生之子金哥出首，说是孤儿。岸贾杀了假孤儿，以为大患除根。至后孤儿长大成人，冤冤相报，杀尽岸贾一门。哎，要存薛氏一后，须得一个小儿可换薛蛟也。",
      "text_length": 182
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00005",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "李敬犹"
      ],
      "text": "观罢前朝心起念，有子可救薛后传。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00006",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李敬犹"
      ],
      "text": "我长子孝德五岁，在花园被妖风摄去，至今并无下落；次子孝思，与薛蛟同年。若去换了薛蛟，我又绝了后代。这便怎么处？哎，昔日程婴若爱其子，如何存得赵氏孤儿？我今若惜孝思，怎救薛氏之后？我兄现有三子，可以接代宗枝。我不免舍子去天牢，换出薛蛟子罢了。",
      "text_length": 120
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00007",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "李敬犹"
      ],
      "text": "暗施阴功天有眼，存个忠义万古传。我不舍子他绝后，忠良无人接香烟。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00008",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "哭",
      "speakers": [
        "李敬犹"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，儿吓。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00009",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "李敬犹下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00010",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四禁子、狱官同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00011",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "狱官"
      ],
      "text": "监狱和班房，牢房有囚床。长板带夹棍，拷打犯法郎。无钱休告状，有钱理也长。若问阴曹府，我是活阎王。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00012",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "狱官"
      ],
      "text": "我，天牢狱官是也。只因薛刚罪大于天，他倒不知逃往哪里去了，可怜他一门尽在天牢。这三百八十五口，分作四监，四监又分四牢，又有许多的字号。武、张二家，命我昼夜紧守。来，天也晚了，小心牢门吓。",
      "text_length": 93
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00013",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四禁子"
      ],
      "text": "吓。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00014",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四家丁抬竹笼子内藏李孝思同上，家院上，李敬犹乘马上。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00015",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "李敬犹"
      ],
      "text": "静悄悄不要高声道，恐惊奸佞查天牢。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00016",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四家丁"
      ],
      "text": "来此天牢监门。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00017",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李敬犹"
      ],
      "text": "众家丁外面伺候。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00018",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四家丁带马同下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00019",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李敬犹"
      ],
      "text": "家院叫开门来。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00020",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "家院放抬盒。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00021",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "家院"
      ],
      "text": "开门。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00022",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "狱官"
      ],
      "text": "看是何人，这时候还来叫门？问他是谁。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00023",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "禁子"
      ],
      "text": "呔，叫门的是谁？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00024",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "家院"
      ],
      "text": "江淮侯前来查监。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00025",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "禁子"
      ],
      "text": "吓，乃是江淮侯前来查监。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00026",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "狱官"
      ],
      "text": "快快开门迎接。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00027",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "禁子"
      ],
      "text": "是。侯爷请进。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00028",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "李敬犹进。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00029",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "狱官"
      ],
      "text": "狱官迎接侯爷。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00030",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李敬犹"
      ],
      "text": "有钦犯在内，速闭监门。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00031",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "狱官"
      ],
      "text": "是、是、是。闭门闭门。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00032",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李敬犹"
      ],
      "text": "薛猛在哪一号？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00033",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "狱官"
      ],
      "text": "在这星字号内。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00034",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李敬犹"
      ],
      "text": "那薛猛诡计多端，本爵要亲自查点。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00035",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "狱官"
      ],
      "text": "但凭侯爷。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00036",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李敬犹"
      ],
      "text": "家院将果盒留下，酒肴尽赏他们去罢。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00037",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "家院"
      ],
      "text": "是。狱官，侯爷赏你酒肴，抬下去饮。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00038",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "狱官"
      ],
      "text": "吓，谢侯爷。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00039",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李敬犹"
      ],
      "text": "不用你们伺候，下去吃酒罢。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00040",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "狱官"
      ],
      "text": "吓，多谢侯爷。来、来、来，抬下去。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00041",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四禁子"
      ],
      "text": "吓。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00042",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四禁子同抬下，狱官下。李敬犹望。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00043",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李敬犹"
      ],
      "text": "快请薛家大爵主出来。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00044",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "家院"
      ],
      "text": "是。大爵主，老爷有请。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00045",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛猛"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00046",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "薛猛、张夫人同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
