      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "张夫人"
      ],
      "text": "可叹公婆在天牢。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00064",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "薛猛"
      ],
      "text": "同监阻隔万山道，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00065",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "哭头",
      "speakers": [
        "薛猛"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，大人吓！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00066",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "张夫人"
      ],
      "text": "父母恩高一旦抛。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00067",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李敬犹"
      ],
      "text": "爵主、夫人请坐了。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00068",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛猛"
      ],
      "text": "大人黑夜到此，有何见教？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00069",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李敬犹"
      ],
      "text": "我等功臣俱已保奏，奈太后不准，无法可救。因此悄悄前来，救令郎出去。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00070",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛猛",
        "张夫人"
      ],
      "text": "大人吓，监中查得紧急，怎么救得小儿出去？",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00071",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李敬犹"
      ],
      "text": "实不相瞒，我儿孝思，与令郎同年。我特来掉换。快抱公子与我。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00072",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "家院"
      ],
      "text": "是。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00073",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "家院抱出薛蛟。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00074",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "家院"
      ],
      "text": "在此。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00075",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛猛"
      ],
      "text": "大人此言差矣。我薛氏并无恩德，如何以亲生代替小儿，舍其一死？薛家就该存后，大人就该绝了宗嗣么？",
      "text_length": 47
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00076",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张夫人"
      ],
      "text": "况令郎清白无罪，为何代替小儿一死？此事断断使不得吓。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00077",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李敬犹"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，爵主、夫人吓！仗义替死，亦为忠义之鬼。实非虚情假意，不可迟延。倘若被人知觉，反为有害。",
      "text_length": 46
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00078",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛猛"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，夫人吓，大人有此天高地厚之恩，你我感恩不尽。大人请上，受我夫妻一拜！",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00079",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李敬犹"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，这就不敢吓。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00080",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "薛猛"
      ],
      "text": "夫妻九泉必相报，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00081",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张夫人"
      ],
      "text": "大人吓！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00082",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 73,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "张夫人"
      ],
      "text": "舍子代死恩天高。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006046_e00083",
      "play_id": "02006046",
      "scene_id": "02006046_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 74,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李敬犹"
      ],
      "text": "爵主、夫人吓！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
